<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA523_05_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema523_su_06.css" />
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema523_05_0003.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_05_su_0003" data-page="ruler-page" data-ruler-scale="0.86">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_pink">
          <div>
            <span lang="y">직선 ㅅㅇ을 대칭축으로 하는 선대칭도형에서 대응변의 길이와 대응각의 크기를 알아봅시다.</span>
            <button type="button" class="icon_supplies" lang="y" data-supplies="pop_supplies_area_1">준비물</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn ruler">자</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn protractor">각도기</button>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <div class="pop_area pop_supplies_area pop_supplies_area_1">
        <div class="supplies_zoom_wrap">
          <button type="button" class="close"></button>
          <div class="supplies_zoom scrollable">
            <div class="supplies_box_wrap">
              <div class="supplies_box">
                <div class="supplies_tit">삼각자, 각도기, 자</div>
                <div class="supplies_contents">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_02_SU/0004_supplies.png" alt="준비물 - 삼각자, 각도기, 자" />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="controller">
              <button class="supplies_scale_down" disabled></button>
              <button class="supplies_scale_up"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">변 ㄱㄴ, 변 ㄴㄷ, 변 ㄷㄹ의 대응변을 각각 찾고, 변의 길이를 재어 비교해 보세요.​</h3>
          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="figure_box">
              <span><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_05_SU/0003_content01.svg" alt="도형이미지" /></span>
              <div class="figure_triangle">
                <span class="txt_1" lang="y">ㄱ</span>
                <span class="txt_2" lang="y">ㄴ</span>
                <span class="txt_3" lang="y">ㄷ</span>
                <span class="txt_4" lang="y">ㄹ</span>
                <span class="txt_5" lang="y">ㅁ</span>
                <span class="txt_6" lang="y">ㅂ</span>
                <span class="txt_7" lang="y">ㅅ</span>
                <span class="txt_8" lang="y">ㅇ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="question_box align_start mt_20">
              <ul class="form_box">
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변 ㄱㄴ</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="ㄱㅂ"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="form_box">
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변 ㄴㄷ</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="ㅂㅁ"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="form_box">
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변 ㄷㄹ</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">변</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="ㅁㄹ"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">㎝</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">각 ㄱㄴㄷ, 각 ㄴㄷㄹ의 대응각을 각각 찾고, 각의 크기를 재어 비교해 보세요.​</h3>
          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="figure_box">
              <span><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_05_SU/0003_content01.svg" alt="도형이미지" /></span>
              <div class="figure_triangle">
                <span class="txt_1" lang="y">ㄱ</span>
                <span class="txt_2" lang="y">ㄴ</span>
                <span class="txt_3" lang="y">ㄷ</span>
                <span class="txt_4" lang="y">ㄹ</span>
                <span class="txt_5" lang="y">ㅁ</span>
                <span class="txt_6" lang="y">ㅂ</span>
                <span class="txt_7" lang="y">ㅅ</span>
                <span class="txt_8" lang="y">ㅇ</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="question_box align_start mt_20">
              <ul class="form_box">
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">각 ㄱㄴㄷ</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="80"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">˚</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">각</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="ㄱㅂㅁ"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="80"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">˚</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <ul class="form_box">
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">각 ㄴㄷㄹ</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">˚</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <div class="vertical1" lang="y">
                    <span lang="y">각</span>
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="ㅂㅁㄹ"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="vertical2">
                    <div class="input_wrap input2">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span lang="y">˚</span>
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">선대칭도형에서 대응변의 길이와 대응각의 크기에 대해 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box mt_20 justify_center">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">선대칭도형은 대응변의 길이와 대응각의 크기가 각각 같습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize">
              <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
              <div>
                <span lang="y">선대칭도형은 </span>
                <button class="reveal_btn margin" lang="y">대응변</button>
                <span lang="y" class="small-gap">의 길이와 </span>
                <button class="reveal_btn margin" lang="y">대응각</button>
                <span lang="y" class="small-gap">의</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span lang="y">크기가 각각 같습니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true" lang="y">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
